  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Bezodpadov&#xE9; spracovanie nebezpe&#x10D;n&#xFD;ch biologick&#xFD;ch odpadov na produkty vhodn&#xE9; pre intenz&#xED;vne ekologick&#xE9; po&#x13E;nohospod&#xE1;rstvo</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Waste-free processing of biohazardous waste into products suitable for intensive organic farming</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Projekt je zameran&#xFD; na osvetu a predstavenie najnov&#x161;&#xED;ch inovat&#xED;vnych technol&#xF3;gii spracovania nebezpe&#x10D;n&#xFD;ch biologick&#xFD;ch odpadov do produktov vyu&#x17E;&#xED;van&#xFD;ch v intenz&#xED;vnom ekologickom po&#x13E;nohospod&#xE1;rstve &#x2013; v rastlinnej v&#xFD;robe (RV) a &#x161;pecializovanej RV. Cie&#x13E;om projektu je uk&#xE1;za&#x165; praktick&#xE9; rie&#x161;enia v kontexte na aproxim&#xE1;ciu eur&#xF3;pskej legislat&#xED;vy v projektovej krajine &#x2013; Ukrajine, ktor&#xE1; doposia&#x13E; nem&#xE1; vyrie&#x161;en&#xFA; problematiku likvid&#xE1;cie nebezpe&#x10D;n&#xFD;ch biologick&#xFD;ch odpadov &#x10D;&#xED;m bezprostredne ohrozuje &#x17E;ivotn&#xE9; prostredie obyvate&#x13E;ov.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project is aimed at raising awareness and present the latest innovative processing technology biohazardous waste into products used in intensive organic farming - in crop production (RV) and RV specialist. The project aims to demonstrate practical solutions in the context of the approximation of EU legislation in the project country - Ukraine, which has so far not resolved the issue of disposal of biohazardous waste which directly threatens the environment population.</narrative>
  </description>
